11:51.040 --> 12:01.560
And also to provide that the TBA might make a manner extension of its service to some

12:01.560 --> 12:02.720
close by REA.

12:02.720 --> 12:08.080
It never has made any more than a manner extension of its service anywhere.

12:08.080 --> 12:11.920
But in order to make a major one that it would have to secure a congressional approval.

12:11.920 --> 12:18.160
But I personally would rather these limitations and other limitations it might come up not

12:18.160 --> 12:24.240
be placed on this self-financing bill.

12:24.240 --> 12:29.240
We will have to have some amendments of this kind in order to get it passed.

12:29.240 --> 12:35.480
I think during the five years the TBA can prove itself and go on as a great agency that it

12:35.480 --> 12:38.480
is and live with these amendments.

12:38.480 --> 12:42.080
Anyway, we're doing everything possible to get the bill passed.

