Japanese court.

13:04.720 --> 13:11.160
And you know what's the strange thing that this goes to show that how individual actions

13:11.160 --> 13:16.800
and issues of this kind determine the attitude and the relationship between nations as much

13:16.800 --> 13:24.040
as the tremendous amount of money that we have spent since the war of visions and visions

13:24.040 --> 13:29.960
of dollars to how to help to 10 and not spend the nation get on her feet.

13:29.960 --> 13:36.440
But some incident like this and it happened very impeccably because our soldiers are well

13:36.440 --> 13:40.320
behaved generally and things like this do not occur.

13:40.320 --> 13:43.560
And this roughed the relationship between nations.

13:44.200 --> 13:51.560
Well Gerard it will be remembered that was accused of killing a Japanese woman and I do

13:51.560 --> 13:57.800
not want to minimize the extent of the seriousness of what he's been charged with and in the extent

13:57.800 --> 13:58.800
whatsoever.

13:58.800 --> 14:06.080
