14:06.080 --> 14:10.720
while on duty and on the reservation there to be fired by court martial.

14:10.720 --> 14:14.400
And they're out on their own and off duty while they'd be fired by the civilian courts

14:14.400 --> 14:17.240
of the country in which they are located.

14:17.240 --> 14:21.600
And that applies reciprocally when some of their soldiers are over here.

14:21.600 --> 14:25.240
The big mistake that's been made is that we have vacillated in the matter.

14:25.240 --> 14:30.000
I personally have information I have he was on duty and on the reservation and he should

14:30.000 --> 14:32.000
have been fired on court martial.

14:32.000 --> 14:36.800
And now a court has come into the case and we all have to wait I think until the Supreme

14:36.800 --> 14:37.800
Court acts.

14:38.440 --> 14:43.480
In any event I hope that by diplomacy the rights of this young man can be preserved.

14:43.480 --> 14:47.960
He's entitled to be fired by court martial and that our relationships will not be

14:47.960 --> 14:50.960
a rapidly damaged between Japan and our country.

14:50.960 --> 14:51.960
That's all for now.

